{"schemaVersion":"gas-shunin-manual-law-explanation-audit/v1","reviewedAt":"2026-07-11","qualification":"gas-shunin-kou","examYear":2022,"sourceQuestionKey":"gas-shunin:kou:2022:law:q15","questionLabel":"問15","sourceQuestionBodyText":"法令で規定されている消費機器に関する調査、保安業務規程及びガス事業者間の連携協力に関する次の記述のうち、誤っているものはいくつあるか。","sourceFile":"output/gas-shunin-kou/questions_json/2022/00_source/question_2022_firestore_2.json","explanationPatchFile":"output/gas-shunin-kou/questions_json/2022/21_explanationText_added/question_2022_firestore_2_explanationText_added.json","sourceCorrectChoiceText":["間違い","正しい","間違い","正しい","正しい"],"patchedCorrectChoiceText":["間違い","正しい","間違い","正しい","正しい"],"correctChoiceTextMatchesSource":true,"choiceReviews":[{"choiceIndex":0,"verdict":"間違い","directBasis":["ガス事業法第159条第3項"],"basisText":"不適合時は是正措置及び未実施時の結果を所有者又は占有者へ通知する。"},{"choiceIndex":1,"verdict":"正しい","directBasis":["同法第160条第2項"],"basisText":"保安業務規程の変更事項を遅滞なく経済産業大臣へ届け出る。"},{"choiceIndex":2,"verdict":"間違い","directBasis":["同条第3項"],"basisText":"変更命令の相手方はガス小売事業者である。"},{"choiceIndex":3,"verdict":"正しい","directBasis":["同条第4項"],"basisText":"ガス小売事業者及び従業者は保安業務規程を守る。"},{"choiceIndex":4,"verdict":"正しい","directBasis":["同法第163条"],"basisText":"ガス事業者は公共安全維持又は災害防止のため連携協力する。"}],"changedFields":["explanationText","sourceExplanationCommonSummary","sourceExplanationChoiceSnippets"],"result":"reviewed_and_rewritten","sourceUrls":["https://laws.e-gov.go.jp/law/329AC0000000051"]}
